    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Experimental validation confirms NIH predictions within ±15% across all COU operating points. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Regulatory submission may proceed using CFD predictions as primary evidence for tolerance sensitivity analysis.",
